: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP QU\u1ea2NG NAM VS B\u00ccNH D\u01af\u01a0NG</strong></u></span></span><br style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1035","checkdouble":"190688"},{"date":"14:42 08/07","title":"C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ramon Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real khi n\u1ea3y sinh \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Calderon c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng`\u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh 5 danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 34 v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng CR7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a Real t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Calderon \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch cho r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch cho r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cN\u1ebfu Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a trong v\u00f2ng 9 n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFlorentino Perez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Real qua c\u00e1c n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebf th\u1eeba t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Iker Casillas v\u00e0 Raul.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng Perez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 anh cao nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn. Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Neymar g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Calderon \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ronaldo ch\u1ecdn Juve</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Juventus l\u1eabn Serie A \u0111ang mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJuventus t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1eady n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Serie A. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Champions League. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t cho l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. V\u1eady n\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/messi-va-ronaldo-xuat-hien-tren-khan-dai-trong-tran-nga-vs-croatia-465-190659.html\">Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-cap-doi-khien-messi-va-ronaldo-cung-phai-ghen-ti-421-190615.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ghen t\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1034","checkdouble":"190689"},{"date":"14:28 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/thu-mon-pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-28-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Thu-mon-Pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-DT-Anh-vao-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 7/7, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u1ed3 h\u1edfi v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh n\u00f3i: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n&quot;.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB Everton \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Sau khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n pha c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea3n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Marcus Berg, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;, Pickford chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Pickford v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2 g\u1eb7p Croatia. Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n t\u00e0i, c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo-421-190677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo-421-190677.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh: T\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 h\u00e3o huy\u1ec1n</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi v\u1ebb m\u1eb7t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luke-shaw-phan-ung-the-nao-khi-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190680.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/luke-shaw-phan-ung-the-nao-khi-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luke-shaw-phan-ung-the-nao-khi-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190680.html\">Luke Shaw ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o khi Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span><br>\r\nLuke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Tam s\u01b0 sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi x\u1ee9 \u0102ng-l\u00ea ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nMang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 - \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay \u0111ang ph\u1