/span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1030","checkdouble":"190695"},{"date":"15:02 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuyen-anh-duoc-khen-het-loi-sau-khi-giup-doi-nha-vao-ban-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed1i qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Pickford \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e0i ba n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pickford\" title=\"Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/3-ly-do-khien-thuy-dien-thua-dang-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Gareth Southgate c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &quot;Pickford cho t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00fd, nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Kieran Tripper hay c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra v\u00e0o nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Pickford&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam s\u01b0, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;Jordan Pickford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chia vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng nhau&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi Jurgen Klinsmann, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng: &quot;\u0110i\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Pickford v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea1o ra c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng 5m50&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Pickford th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 HLV Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n Janne Andersson th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Pickford l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Jordan Pickford s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau 52 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-28-nam-421-190692.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/thu-mon-pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-28-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-28-nam-421-190692.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m?</span><br>\r\nG\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luke-shaw-phan-ung-the-nao-khi-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190680.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/luke-shaw-phan-ung-the-nao-khi-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luke-shaw-phan-ung-the-nao-khi-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190680.html\">Luke Shaw ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o khi Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span><br>\r\nLuke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Tam s\u01b0 sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-thuy-dien-thua-dang-dt-anh-466-190654.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/3-ly-do-khien-thuy-dien-thua-dang-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-thuy-dien-thua-dang-dt-anh-466-190654.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thua \u0111\u1eafng \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c Anh trong ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Janne...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1029","checkdouble":"190696"},{"date":"16:22 08/07","title":"Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Juventus \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 CR7.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m quan c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric cho r\u1eb1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nghi\u0303 anh \u00e2\u0301y se\u0303 r\u01a1\u0300i Real Madrid. Ronaldo la\u0300 c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 xu\u00e2\u0301t s\u0103\u0301c nh\u00e2\u0301t th\u00ea\u0301 gi\u01a1\u0301i, t\u00f4i mu\u00f4\u0301n anh \u00e2\u0301y \u01a1\u0309 la\u0323i vi\u0300 \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u na\u0300y co\u0301 y\u0301 nghi\u0303a r\u00e2\u0301t quan tro\u0323ng v\u1edbi CLB.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ha\u0303y ch\u01a1\u0300 xem \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u gi\u0300 se\u0303 xa\u0309y ra. Se\u0303 th\u00e2\u0323t tuy\u00ea\u0323t v\u01a1\u0300i n\u00ea\u0301u Ronaldo ti\u00ea\u0301p tu\u0323c g\u0103\u0301n bo\u0301 v\u01a1\u0301i Real Madrid. T\u00f4i ch\u0103\u0309ng th\u00ea\u0309 t\u01b0\u01a1\u0323ng t\u01b0\u01a1\u0323ng n\u00f4\u0309i hi\u0300nh a\u0309nh anh \u00e2\u0301y khoa\u0301c a\u0301o \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng kha\u0301c\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Du\u0300 tin \u0111\u00f4\u0300n Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhan nh\u1ea3n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ca\u0309 Juventus l\u00e2\u0303n Real Madrid \u0111\u00ea\u0300u ch\u01b0a co\u0301 \u0111\u00f4\u0323ng tha\u0301i chi\u0301nh th\u01b0\u0301c na\u0300o v\u00ea\u0300 vi\u00ea\u0323c n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e2\u0323m chi\u0301, c\u01b0\u0323u CEO AC Milan, Adriano Galliani m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng cho bi\u00ea\u0301t \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a h\u00ea\u0300 nghe b\u00e2\u0301t c\u01b0\u0301 th\u00f4ng tin na\u0300o v\u00ea\u0300 th\u01b0\u01a1ng vu\u0323 Cristiano Ronaldo du\u0300 m\u00ecnh la\u0300 ba\u0323n th\u00e2n cu\u0309a Florentino Perez.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\">C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ramon Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real khi n\u1ea3y sinh \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bao-than-real-xat-muoi-vao-vet-thuong-long-cua-neymar-sau-tran-thua-bi-421-190600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/bao-than-real-xat-muoi-vao-vet-thuong-long-cua-neymar-sau-tran-thua-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bao-than-real-xat-muoi-vao-vet-thuong-long-cua-neymar-sau-tran-thua-bi-421-190600.html\">B\u00e1o th\u00e2n Real x\u00e1t mu\u1ed1i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Neymar sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Neymar, \u00f4ng Tomas Roncero -T\u1ed5ng bi\u00ean t\u1eadp t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Real, AS kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao Brazil c\u00f2n l\u00e2u m\u1edbi s\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid-180-190592.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/2/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid-180-190592.html\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nJuventus mua Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1028","checkdouble":"190697"},{"date":"09:22 08/07","title":"HLV Croatia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-len-tieng-thach-thuc-anh-o-ban-ket.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0110T Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho NHM m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau 2-2 trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o Croatia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-len-tieng-thach-thuc-anh-o-ban-ket.PNG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nHLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dalic th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Dalic v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zlatko Dalic phat bieu ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ha-dan-mach-vao-tu-ket-hlv-croatia-noi-gi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cAnh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Croatia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 50-50. Ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung\u00a0 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1027","checkdouble":"190669"},{"date":"09:33 08/07","title":"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi t\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ligue 1, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNabil Fekir r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Fekir, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Liverpool th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martial, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lyon kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Fekir cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nabil Fekir\" title=\"Nabil Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Fekir s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Lyon, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Fekir h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Lyon, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1026","checkdouble":"190670"},{"date":"09:55 08/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/everton-va-tottenham-muon-mua-mina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho Chelsea c\u1ea3. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Conte.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/David-Luiz-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh David Luiz s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Luiz c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m David Luiz</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Porto v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 David Luiz ra \u0111i. N\u1ebfu The Blues nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Napoli-muon-mua-David-Luiz-cua-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin \u0111\u1ed3n Porto mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Benfica v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u1edf\u00a0m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a David Luiz, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do r\u1eddi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1025","checkdouble":"190671"},{"date":"10:15 08/07","title":"Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aston Villa bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Aston Villa gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 play-off, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Middlesbrough \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Fulham song sau c\u00f9ng thua 0-1. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Premier League khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Tony Xia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Aston Villa s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1edbi tai nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Jack Grealish.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho sao tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Aston Villa ra gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Grealish. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua c\u00f9ng Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18, Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 Tottenham hay Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Grealish. Ph\u00eda Aston Villa hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/9/7/hlv-hodgson-giuc-sao-tre-aston-villa-som-chon-dtqg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Mirror, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng Liverpool b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd \u00e2m th\u1ea7m theo s\u00e1t Grealish v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua kim ti\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Philippe Coutinho, hi\u1ec7n Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino, HLV Klopp v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-khong-nen-chieu-mo-forsberg-172-190458.html\">Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-len-tieng-choc-tuc-man-utd-172-190403.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1024","checkdouble":"190672"},{"date":"10:56 08/07","title":"Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-david-luiz-172-189742.html\" target=\"_blank\">Los\u00a0Blancos quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mane</span> c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Sadio-Mane-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real quan t\u00e2m Mane\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Mane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Firmino v\u00e0 Salah h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eafc b\u00e9n. Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Real hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra 33 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mane t\u1eeb Southampton, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mane t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp noi ve Mane\" title=\"Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00f4ng tin Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9. Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Liverpool.\"</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Klopp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1023","checkdouble":"190673"}]}